Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何も怖くなんてないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手にしたものを失うくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}争いを待つ事を繰り返して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何もかもを欲しがっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷えるものの誓い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未だ見ぬ世界を創りだす事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朽ち果てていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}哀しい夢を遮るものは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自らの闇だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel何処からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}流れる景色変わらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}音もなく解き放つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}畏れ断ち切り何時からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}高鳴る鼓動止まらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}易しくも消し去って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我並非是在膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去曾經的擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}等待著周而復始的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}掠奪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曾經渴求著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}立下極易迷失的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必將創造出人們從未見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直至此生的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}阻擋哀傷之夢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是自身的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel會有一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變幻之景不再更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悄然間將自身解放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}切斷畏懼後不知從何開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}內心的悸動無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又輕易地將其熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向かい風吹く 一寸先 予想も出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心不乱 キミに付いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一期一会の宝を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}足が震えても 止まらない 胸の高鳴り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前人未到 旅はいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全身全霊 エンジン全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絶対キミを守る どんなリスクがあるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}‘絶対'なんかないさ チカラを尽くそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思い切り吸い込んだ 果てしない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}望遠鏡覗けば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}カリスマティックな闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うねる波の迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(365,330)}ラビリンス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 幽閉された星を解き放つため
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}キミと旅立とう 月が明日へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(375,330)}あす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迎風而立 未來無法預料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心一意 追隨在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誓取一生的珍寶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}即便腳步顫抖不已 也難阻心中的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前无古人 隨時啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全心全力 火力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕對要保護你 無論艱難險阻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凡事沒有絕對 但會竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}徹底掉入無盡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}從望遠鏡中看去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充滿誘惑的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曲曲折折的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 解放幽閉之星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與你同行 月引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 人們就對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而走在那眾妖之前 統領著百鬼夜行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們稱其為妖怪的總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是如此稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛受到某種指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:07.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生和他的同伴踏入了捩眼山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:15.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是奴良組裡的武鬥派 牛鬼組的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:22.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛鬼組手下的身影 逼近了已被分散的陸生等人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:28.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生等人的命運到底會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人 是奴良組的小頭目奴良陸生的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若你明知故犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.73,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,300)}新月之夜黑暗湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴良陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從身體內部不斷上湧 血在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:00.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:03.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說連一個人都沒看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是少主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:42.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:48.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您退下 那傢伙是真心想殺了少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是應該老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我必須保護少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:55.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟傳聞一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟要靠那樣弱小的侍從保護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼三代頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是牛鬼的手下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道這樣很無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我們老大的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 奴良陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:45.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下受柚羅大人之命前來護駕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裡會有式神使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:57.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我還想早于牛頭丸將勝利彙報給牛鬼大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:05:59.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處亂飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:13.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:21.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊 你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:25.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在跟誰說話嗎 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:29.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不知道我們鴉天狗一族的名號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉…鴉天狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的看家人為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 少主好像不在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷襲女浴池的妖怪嗎 真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰陽師 現在暫時休戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的人給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 我有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不聽話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:02.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊鼠事件 少主的所在之處 把你知道的都說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:05.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救救我 陰陽師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把這些傢伙退治了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:21.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:33.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:36.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人說到了「少主」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:02.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是破綻百出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的刀在哭泣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:24.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的膽小鬼怎麼可能贏得過我牛頭丸的爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:25.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:34.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 明明還是白天的模樣 但為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:43.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙沒覺醒的話應該只是個普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:53.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼算是對你略表敬意 就讓你見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們牛鬼組的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛頭陰魔爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:10.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:46.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:10:00.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛鬼組有著操縱 迷惑人心再將之砍殺的「怵」之代紋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能輸給區區人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:08.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「區區人類」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就結束了 奴良陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會被不是妖怪的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上流淌著血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:39.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡的…總大將之血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是由我兒子們傳來的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:52.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您意下如何 總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人問寒山道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒山妖怪在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天冰未釋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:15.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日出霧朦朦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似我何由屆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與君心不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君心若似我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得到其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:05.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 雪女和青田坊他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去泡溫泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:15.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿青去做了護衛 小僧卻得待在這裡 真是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們平時也沒有變裝陪在少主身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:28.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我乾脆也陪著少主去學校好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以穿水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:34.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個有年齡限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴆大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙的有什麼要緊事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:58.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生他…不 少主他去了捩眼山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:06.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖知此言不妥 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:14.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在下鴆仍覺得最近的牛鬼不太平常 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼放任不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就交給陸生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給少主？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:32.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛鬼是我給予了很大信賴的部下之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:37.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我的孫子來傾聽一下他的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有異議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:52.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的身體 去了也救不了少主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:59.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下鴆 賭上交杯之誓 永遠都會相信少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一時半會動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 自己身體的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:34.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在晚上 就會變成這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息吧 雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚羅超厲害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:08.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚羅要是不在的話 我們肯定玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:15.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 那個鳥人一樣的傢伙不也很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超厲害啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他們的存在本身就很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:32.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會在我不在的時候碰到妖怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:35.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及川同學 及川同學在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:42.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 奴良同學他們還有加奈都怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的吧 而且那幫鳥人也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:01.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天 走了這麼久怎麼誰也沒有碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學他們 還有及川和陸生同學他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:27.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 早知道就不來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:02.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:55.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新月的時候 對人類來說太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:12.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及川同學 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:15.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 她就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:21.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是陸生同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:32.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 還是快點回去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:43.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要變天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是害怕的話就閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:02.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:07.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就一直知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:09.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:36.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想些什麼 牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我還能挺住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的確繼承了總大將的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭滑腦的 四處出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭滑腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚羅你一個人住的話怎麼解決吃飯問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有便利店 比如便利店啊 還有便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:37.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話今晚來我家吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 滑頭鬼之孫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅若丸 淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
